Introduction

HeyGirls was a South Korean girl group under MOAI Entertainment. Originally called Black Queen, they gained some recognition after appearing on Mnet's talent show Superstar K3 before officially debuting on October 19, 2012 with the single "Good Girl".

On December 26, 2023, MOAI announced the group's disbandment, and that the sub-unit 1CHU would become an independent group.
